    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007114_3_5011-5041",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "5011-5041",
      "markText": "葡萄的卷须有一点淡淡的甜味。这东西如果腌成咸菜，大概不难吃。",
      "totalCount": 646,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007114&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5011&rangeEnd=5041",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d69322b0813ab6947g01416e?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5011&rangeEnd=5041"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007114_3_5138-5186",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "5138-5186",
      "markText": "都说梨花像雪，其实苹果花才像雪，雪是厚重的，不是透明的。梨花像什么呢？——梨花的瓣子是月亮做的。",
      "totalCount": 429,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007114&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5138&rangeEnd=5186",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d69322b0813ab6947g01416e?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5138&rangeEnd=5186"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007114_3_6363-6389",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "6363-6389",
      "markText": "九月的果园像一个生过孩子的少妇，宁静、幸福，而慵懒。",
      "totalCount": 425,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007114&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6363&rangeEnd=6389",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d69322b0813ab6947g01416e?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6363&rangeEnd=6389"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007114_4_12111-12181",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "12111-12181",
      "markText": "栀子花粗粗大大，又香得掸都掸不开，于是为文雅人不取，以为品格不高。栀子花说：“去你妈的，我就是要这样香，香得痛痛快快，你们他妈的管得着吗！”",
      "totalCount": 390,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007114&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=12111&rangeEnd=12181",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d69322b0813ab6947g01416e?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=12111&rangeEnd=12181"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007114_3_2802-2852",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2802-2852",
      "markText": "这故事是一个种葡萄的果农告诉我的。他说，中国的农民是很能干的。什么事都瞒不过中国人。中国人一看就会。",
      "totalCount": 378,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007114&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2802&rangeEnd=2852",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d69322b0813ab6947g01416e?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2802&rangeEnd=2852"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007114_3_10296-10366",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "10296-10366",
      "markText": "女同学吃胡萝卜的就更多了。她们常常一把一把地买来吃。一把有十多根。她们一边谈着克列斯丁娜·罗赛蒂的诗、布朗底的小说，一边咯吱咯吱地咬胡萝卜。",
      "totalCount": 360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007114&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=10296&rangeEnd=10366",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d69322b0813ab6947g01416e?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=10296&rangeEnd=10366"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007114_3_5854-5950",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "5854-5950",
      "markText": "下过大雨，你来看看葡萄园吧，那叫好看！白的像白玛瑙，红的像红宝石，紫的像紫水晶，黑的像黑玉。一串一串，饱满、磁棒、挺括，璀璨琳琅。你就把《说文解字》里的带玉字偏旁的字都搬了来吧，那也不够用呀！",
      "totalCount": 342,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007114&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5854&rangeEnd=5950",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d69322b0813ab6947g01416e?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5854&rangeEnd=5950"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007114_3_1005-1033",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1005-1033",
      "markText": "人说，要大穗，要香甜多汁，于是谷子和葡萄就成了现在这样。",
      "totalCount": 322,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007114&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1005&rangeEnd=1033",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d69322b0813ab6947g01416e?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1005&rangeEnd=1033"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007114_3_581-648",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "581-648",
      "markText": "一个学农业的同志告诉我：谷子是从狗尾巴草变来的，葡萄是从爬山虎变来的。我听了，觉得很有意思。谷子和狗尾巴草，葡萄和爬山虎，长得是很像。",
      "totalCount": 312,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007114&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=581&rangeEnd=648",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d69322b0813ab6947g01416e?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=581&rangeEnd=648"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007114_3_2004-2052",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2004-2052",
      "markText": "“当其朱夏涉秋，尚有余暑、醉酒宿酲，掩露而食，甘而不饴，脆而不酸，冷而不寒，味长汁多，除烦解倦”",
      "totalCount": 280,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007114&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2004&rangeEnd=2052",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d69322b0813ab6947g01416e?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2004&rangeEnd=2052"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007114_3_25260-25286",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "25260-25286",
      "markText": "四川北碚的怪味胡豆味道真怪，酥、脆、咸、甜、麻、辣。",
      "totalCount": 247,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007114&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=25260&rangeEnd=25286",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d69322b0813ab6947g01416e?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=25260&rangeEnd=25286"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007114_3_7220-7280",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "7220-7280",
      "markText": "一到冬天，要检查几次。不是怕别的，怕老鼠打了洞。葡萄窖里很暖和，老鼠爱往这里面钻。它倒是暖和了，咱们的葡萄可就受了冷啦！",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007114&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7220&rangeEnd=7280",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d69322b0813ab6947g01416e?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7220&rangeEnd=7280"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007114_8_18523-18572",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "18523-18572",
      "markText": "我很想喝一碗咸菜慈姑汤。 我想念家乡的雪。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007114&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=18523&rangeEnd=18572",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d69322b0813ab6947g01416e?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=18523&rangeEnd=18572"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007114_3_13558-13620",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "13558-13620",
      "markText": "我们在长沙，想尝尝毛泽东在火宫殿吃过的臭豆腐，循味跟踪，臭味渐浓。“快了，快到了，闻到臭味了嘛！”到了眼前，是一个公共厕所！",
